Class NameSpaceDefinition

java.lang.Object
  resources.RootClass
      translator.NameSpaceDefinition

public class NameSpaceDefinition
extends RootClass

Handle a name space definition extracted from some XML header The namespace declaration looks like xmlns:nsName=http://.... The declaration is stored with nsName extracted with a capturing group
